citation: Proclamation under the Supreme Court Civil Procedure Amendment Act 2019 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Supreme Court Civil Procedure Amendment Act 2019

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Supreme Court Civil Procedure Amendment Act 2019 , fix 9 September 2019 as the day on which that Act commences.

27 August 2019

C. WARNER

Governor

By Her Excellency's Command,

ELISE ARCHER

Minister for Justice

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 4 September 2019

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Justice.
